name: 6 Tribal Shields - Gaya Tribe
description:
Gaya ~ ( Tribe of Wealth )

Unified in their resourcefulness, this Tribe has inexhaustible riches. The World is their bounty and they only grow wealthier as the years roll by. Every son and daughter knows how to turn their hand at a task that will inevitably bear fruits. 
They are comrades, soul mates and believers. Honourable, faithful and gifted.
There is no lack in their World. Only prosperity, growth and the knowledge of giving and receiving.
Warriors of Wealth and the Word.
